  "description": "<p><strong>Fresh grad? Career switcher? We provide full training — just bring your energy and drive!⚡</strong><br /><br /></p><p>✨What you’ll do:</p><ul><li>Engage customers and represent client brands</li><li>Build strong connections and deliver a positive experience</li><li>Managing sales</li><li>Work closely with clients to help with business development</li></ul><p>🫵Who we’re looking for:</p><ul><li>Outgoing, confident, and people-oriented</li><li>Team player with a drive to learn and grow</li><li>No experience required — training provided!</li></ul><p>💰What we will provide:</p><ul><li>Career advancement & leadership pathways</li><li>Hands-on sales, marketing & client management skills</li><li>Fun, supportive, and energetic team culture</li><li>Attractive incentives + travel opportunities</li></ul><p>APPLY TODAY TO FIND OUT MORE!🔈🔈🔈</p>",
